  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK129">
<l>tīyiṉāṟ cuṭṭapu ṇuḷḷāṟu māṟātē</l>
<l>nāviṉāṟ cuṭṭa vaṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The burn left by fire heals within; what does not heal</l>
<l>is the burning scar left by the tongue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
